rComments: I am NOT a fan of this prof. She's IMMENSELY condescending and extremely rude to the students. She's a tough grader, and she makes you feel like you don't belong in the program. I hated this class because of her. If you can avoid her, DO IT.

rComments: She's a really caring professor! She does her very best to explain confusing French concepts. She also has a great sense of humor and is there for her students! As long as you read the textbook and do the exercises and pay attention, you'll do fine.
